the lore of AJAY:
  you are apart of an organisation called SEA (SpaceExplorationAgency)
  crew members are tasked with the discovery and exploration of new planets you 
  are tasked with the exploration of the planet "Earth"
  every time a crew members memory gets erased the only left is there task getting back to the ship and exploring as much as possible in
  the procces, and also not die and stuff..
  
